cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

The paper deals with deep convolutional networks and their success in image classification tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the nature of the learned representations, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a new architecture, which involves solving ill-conditioned problems, which could fall under neural networks (cs.NE) and data structures (cs.DS).
